name: NINUY - Name Is Not Unlocked Yet
name_original: NINUY - Name Is Not Unlocked Yet
description:
NINUY is a 3D Platformer that puts the player in control of Kiko, a weak character who will gain abilities while traversing through a cute platforming environment.

NINUY is a 2018 Global Game Jam game. It can also be found here:
https://globalgamejam.org/2018/games/ninuy-name-not-unlocked-yet

It was created by:

Xandra van Antwerpen - Art - XandraVanAntwerpen.com 

Justin van Oort - Tech Design - JustinVanOort.com
